    "The prompt should always be in code block.",
    "The prompt should end with \"this is a draft.",
    "Please adjust so that it works for you.\"",
    "• Explain after the code block prompt (and not in the code block) that this is a draft and that the teacher should copy and paste the prompt into a new chat and test it out to see if it helps them complete the task.",
    "They should refine the initial prompt so that it is useful for them and so that it creates a repeatable process."
